snippet.title: Taito Milestones is back for a thrilling new compilation of TAITO’s nostalgic gems!
snippet.description:
Relive the spirit of these action-packed classics, and reignite the flame of TAITO’s nostalgic gems in this thrilling new compilation, exclusively for Nintendo Switch, physical and digital.

Gems included in the collection:
- The NewZealand Story (1988)
- Kiki Kaikai (1986)
- Darius 2 (Three Screen Arcade  Version) (1989)
- Gun Frontier (1990)
- Ben Bero Beh (1984)
- The Legend of Kage (1985)
- Liquid Kids (Mizubaku Adventure) (1990)
- Solitary Fighter (1991)
- Dinorex (1992)
- Metal Black (1991)

Pre order now at https://www.iningames.com/games/taito-milestones-2/
